#5800
The entrance to the City of Stone~
You find yourself standing before a city with enormous, grey houses. 
Everything inside this impressive city seems to be made out of stone, and
although thousands or people could easily have fitted in here, you see no
signs of life.  The wind seems to have gotten stronger, and you almost hear
it making a sad yet frightening tune as it blows through this depressing
city.  You feel an urge to turn around and run as you never ran before, but
if you manage to suppress it you can look north, to see if there is a way
into this godforsaken place.  
~
