Some kind of store~
Once you enter through the doorway you immediately recognise this place
as some kind of store.  Shelves of stone are everywhere, but although no one
seems to have been here for ages there is no sign of cobwebs or dust.  This
cursed place doesn't even smell!  Maybe it's best to return home, because
your sanity seems to get dented and bent by all this.  The shelves are
empty, the only signs of movement is the furious howls of the wind outside. 
