#5813
A podium of sorts~
Three small steps lead up to the middle of this huge room, creating a
podium of sorts.  The sound of your steps bounces between the walls and you
notice even the echo sounds dull.  Once in a while the wind hits the
entrance way with full force and the sound is turned into a grotesque
soulless scream.  The whole room is stone grey, not a hint of color anywhere
just like the rest of the city you have seen so far.  Even your clothes and
equipment seem to be fading in color as if some vampiric being was feeding
upon it.  On the walls hang huge decorations.  They could have been giant
mats if it wasn't for the fact that they are made of stone.  To the west you
see the end of the hall, the way to the east provides you with the option of
stepping outside once again.  
