#5818
Abrupt end of the Stonebridge~
This close to the building the wind suddenly changes direction, pushing
you forward instead of backward.  You realize just in time that a section in
the bridge is gone, and manage to save yourself from a fall to your death by
throwing yourself backwards.  The gigantic building ahead seems so close, if
you only could get across this hole in the bridge, but with the wind raging
it's too dangerous to try.  The building stands tall ahead of you, gates
looking like a giant mouth.  For a while you think you can hear wicked
laughter, but that must have been your imagination.  You face the fact that
the only thing you can do at this point is head back to the city.  
